        "subject": "LU-11554 som: Make stat() work with LSOM",
        "message": "LU-11554 som: Make stat() work with LSOM\n\nCurrently, stat() does not work with LSOM yet, so using \"ls -l\" or\n\"mdtest\" for testing could not exercise the LSOM.\nThis patch adds a lctl interface:\n\tlctl set_param llite.*.lsom=1\nto make stat() behavior selectable to use LSOM data as returned\nfile's size and blocks for stat() system call.\n\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Ia5f2bb47b50df5e0d7ccd74efefcdd8e493b91af\n"
      },
